I watched this one just now... really a great entertainer... deals with relationship between a father and dad , a odd love story , a coming of age of hero intrested in music...  i think director likes the saying "whenever story starts , the logic ends" because many coincidential incidents and persons in a right order makes up the story... eventhough the screenplay is unbelivable , the way the story is presented makes us engaged in the movie... the humerous and comical elements in the movie actually succed in making us laugh at many points but not fully... each character is given somewhat a importance in story... rishi kapoor, aniruth, amyra all have given their best... as the stories deal with so many elements such as sentiment , romance , friendship and so , the screen presence of actors other than amyra , rishi kapoor and aniruth are not so long... scenes depicting old delhi is magical and the concept of that old delhi memories are plesant...  music could have been better... on the whole a well entertaining movie...
